        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th><%= IsrAgreement::ISR_IA_STATUS_LABELS[ 10 ] %></th>
            <td>An IA is marked <%= help_term IsrAgreement::ISR_IA_STATUS_LABELS[ 10 ] %> when 
            during the creation (workflow) of an IA, the IA was found to be not applicable or
            not useful.</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
