    </div>
    <p>The various statistics based on the status of IFs, IAs, and IA Records are documented
    in the help text for <%= link_to_help :isr_agreements, IsrAgreement.model_name.human %>.</p>
    <h3>Status from Responsibility and Validation Steps (RS/VS) - Proposal</h3>
    <p>Since Responsiblity and Validation Steps are implemented as Task/Issue/Action Item Lists,
    the status from these lists is could be an agregation of the individual items: Each item can
    be either 'open' or it is 'closed' ('waiting' should be considered 'open', 'obsolete' should be
    considered 'closed'). A list of Resolution (or Validation) Steps is thus either 'open' (one or
    more items is still 'open') or 'closed' (all items are 'closed').</p>
